    "longBusinessSummary": "Saudi Printing and Packaging Co. provides printing and packaging services in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. The company operates through printing, packaging, and other segments. It also engages in printing newspapers, magazines, and books and printing on plastics and commercial labels. In addition, the company manufactures and sells paper and plastic cups; bottles and caps; and plastic products and packaging materials. Further, it also engages in management and investment activities; prints on plastic and commercial posters; and offers tools and raw materials. The company was formerly known as Madina Printing and Publishing Company and changed its name to Saudi Printing and Packaging Co. in May 2006. The company was founded in 1963 and is headquartered in Riyadh, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.",
